<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2020-12-03/doc-iiznezxs5008949.shtml">必胜客创始人弗兰克・卡尼去世</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384101" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>界面消息，美国披萨连锁品牌必胜客（Pizzahut）创始人之一弗兰克・卡尼（Frank Carney）于当地时间 12 月 2 日凌晨 4 点 30 分因肺炎病逝，享年 82 岁。卡尼近日才从新冠肺炎中康复，他已身患阿兹海默症十多年。</p>
<p>弗兰克与哥哥于 1958 年在堪萨斯州威奇托市，开始携手创建必胜客。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/tDG_i62Fx21svAqCj74v_g">元气森林月销售额一度破 4 亿</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384102" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>食品板援引业内人士消息称，虽然疫情让国内企业「很受伤」，但元气森林今年的月销售额一度破 4 亿元，完成 25 亿的年销售目标问题不大。</p>
<p>而就在前不久召开的经销商大会上，元气森林也透露了 2021 年的线下渠道销售目标，从今年的 21 亿提升到明年的 75 亿。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release">奥利奥和 Lady Gaga 推出合作款饼干</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384103" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>奥利奥和 Lady Gaga 合作推出特别版奥利奥饼干。该新品设计灵感来自 Lady Gaga 的专辑《Chromatica》，饼干颜色为粉红色，并印有对应图案，饼干的夹心奶油也换成了绿色。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release">万代推出《新世纪福音战士》电子宠物机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384104" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1.jpg" alt="" width="1400" height="933" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1.jpg 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，万代推出《新世纪福音战士》主题电子宠物机，玩家可以从中育成主要角色：渚薰、真希波和绫波零。</p>
<p>该系列现在已经可在 Premium BANDAI 官网预订，定价为 2530 日元（约人民币 160 元）。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%2300%E5%90%8E%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E7%9C%BC%E7%BA%BF%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F4%E5%80%8D%23&amp;Refer=top">00 后男生眼线消费增速是女生 4 倍</a></h4>
<p>统计数据显示，2020 年 00 后男生彩妆消费增速已远超 00 后女生。</p>
<p>其中，00 后男生购买粉底液的增速是女生的 2 倍，眼线的增速是女生的 4 倍。最爱买眼妆产品的是广东男生，排名前三的城市分别是 ：深圳、揭阳、汕头。</p>
<p>网友：「感觉很多男孩已经达到化妆的最高境界，一般人看不出他们化了妆。」「增速快不代表总量多啊，女生原本消费基数就很大。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357583" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>一起看个展：《幻景：当代艺术与增强现实》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383844" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/79c64dfe618c4a858a4364bb6fc623c1.gif" alt="" width="360" height="640" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />  UCCA 尤伦斯当代艺术中心 · 北京</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/231b.png" alt="⌛" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />  2020.11.28 &#8211; 2021.2.10</strong></p>
<p>UCCA 和 Acute Art 合作打造了这次 AR 艺术特展，带来了妮娜・香奈尔・阿布尼、达伦・巴德、曹斐、奥拉维尔・埃利亚松、KAWS 和阿丽莎・柯维德的作品。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383845" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>本次展出的都是 AR 作品，需结合智能手机观看。UCCA 馆内也为观众免费提供 iPhone 12 系列手机，以方便所有参观者体验本次展出的 AR 艺术作品。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383848" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/exhibit.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="859" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/exhibit.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/exhibit-360x258.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/exhibit-768x550.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/exhibit-1024x733.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<h4>本周上映</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383854" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/cover23.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="1152" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/cover23.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/cover23-360x346.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/cover23-768x737.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/cover23-1024x983.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
➜苹果被罚  7800 多万元？都是防水宣传惹的祸！
https://www.ifanr.com/1383792?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	20421
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383832" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23.png" alt="" width="2320" height="1298" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23.png 2320w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23-1024x573.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2320px) 100vw, 2320px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">“啊！”</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">随着我的一声惨叫，新买不到半个月的 iPhone 12 mini 从手里滑进了满是水的浴缸，我的大脑空白了那么一瞬间，然后才条件反射似的赶紧把手机捞上来。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383803" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip11.png" alt="" width="2322" height="1244" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip11.png 2322w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip11-360x193.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip11-768x411.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip11-1024x549.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2322px) 100vw, 2322px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 事发突然没拍照，大概就是这样的情形</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">把 iPhone 12 mini 捞出水面的那一刻，我的脑子里突然闪过一个念头，现在的 iPhone 都有 IP68 级抗水性能，才掉进水里这么会儿，擦干应该就好了。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">就在我仔细检查手机进水情况的时候，iPhone 12 mini 自动亮了屏，随后 faceID 识别出我的脸展开了一条推送，原来是某资讯 app 推送的一条信息：苹果因防水问题被罚 1000 万欧元。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">我……</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">苹果被罚 1000 万欧？是的。</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">据外媒报道，意大利竞争管理局（AGCM）对苹果公司处以 1000 万欧元（约 7853 万元人民币）罚款，原因是苹果对 iPhone 的防水功能提出了误导性的主张，受影响的 iPhone 型号可以追溯到 2017 年的 iPhone 8 和 iPhone 8 Plus。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383833" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip24.png" alt="" width="1755" height="421" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip24.png 1755w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip24-360x86.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip24-768x184.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip24-1024x246.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1755px) 100vw, 1755px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">AGCM 批评苹果对 iPhone 防水性的说法不够清楚，它表示，关于 iPhone 可以在长达四米的深度下拥有长达 30 分钟的防水功能的说法仅适用于某些情况，例如用纯净水进行的受控实验室测试。<strong>该监管机构还批评了苹果公司的免责声明，称尽管销售了具有防水功能的手机，但水损不属于 iPhone 保修的一部分。</strong></span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">早在 2018 年，AGCM 曾因苹果对电池老化设备限制性能的做法，给苹果开出了 1000 万欧元的罚单。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">IP67/68 到底是什么？</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">在苹果官网商品介绍页里，几乎目前在售的 iPhone 都会把抗水性能作为重要卖点之一，通过生动的可视化图片向顾客传达「iPhone 抗水性能强悍」的信息。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383806" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip14.png" alt="" width="2386" height="1380" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip14.png 2386w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip14-360x208.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip14-768x444.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip14-1024x592.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2386px) 100vw, 2386px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">目前大家比较熟悉的 IP67/68 标准，IP、678 分别代表什么呢？</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">IP 是 Ingress Protection 的缩写，IP 等级是针对电气设备外壳对异物侵入的防护等级，来源是国际电工委员会的标准 IEC 60529。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">评估外壳防固体和防水性能如何，主要看 IP XX 的后面两位数字 XX，第一位 X 是防尘等级，从 0 到 6，最高等级为 6；第 2 位 X 是防水等级，从 0 到 9，最高等级为 9。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383814" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1174.png" alt="" width="586" height="368" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1174.png 586w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1174-360x226.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">中国相关测试依据为 </span>GB<span class="ql-author-24360693">∕T</span> 4208-2017 外壳防护等级（IP 代码）<span class="ql-author-24360693">标准要求，对各类产品的外壳防护等级进行合格评定性判定试验。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383807" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip7.png" alt="" width="1416" height="964" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip7.png 1416w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip7-360x245.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip7-768x523.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip7-1024x697.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1416px) 100vw, 1416px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383808" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip8.png" alt="" width="1418" height="858" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip8.png 1418w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip8-360x218.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip8-768x465.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip8-1024x620.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1418px) 100vw, 1418px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383809" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip9.png" alt="" width="1414" height="402" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip9.png 1414w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip9-360x102.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip9-768x218.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip9-1024x291.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1414px) 100vw, 1414px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">理论上，符合中国 IP68 标准的硬件设备，应当做到无灰尘进入，且持续潜水后外壳浸水量不致达有害程度。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">IP68 有定义，为何用户有疑问？</span></strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383822" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip19.png" alt="" width="2320" height="1182" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip19.png 2320w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip19-360x183.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip19-768x391.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip19-1024x522.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2320px) 100vw, 2320px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">从理论定义看，IP68 的很多地方规范得「不清不楚」，可能是考虑到实操和商业等因素，部分表述留有很多空间，商家的表述也比较笼统。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">1. 测试环境和现实环境有差距</strong></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383813" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1173.png" alt="" width="1418" height="416" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1173.png 1418w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1173-360x106.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1173-768x225.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1173-1024x300.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1418px) 100vw, 1418px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">手机作为高频和高移动率的智能硬件，需要面对各种不同且不断变化的生活环境。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">比如，一个小时前用户还在办公室刷微博，一个小时后就回到家在厨房里看着手机学炒菜，过一会儿又把手机放到浴室外放歌曲，这个季度还在「没有冬天」的广东省使用，过年的时候就回到平均温度零下十几度的黑龙江过年，平常生活在低海拔地区，「说走就走」立即就到西藏旅游。这让一些符合 IP68 标准的设备在现实场景中「翻车」，极端情况下甚至一点点水可能就会让设备进水损坏。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383815" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip17.png" alt="" width="2322" height="1256" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip17.png 2322w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip17-360x195.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip17-768x415.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip17-1024x554.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2322px) 100vw, 2322px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 特殊条件下，也许一杯水就能导致手机进水</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">用户只是普通消费者，不懂这些专业知识，大多数人会认为「某品牌说好的 IP68 就是忽悠人的」，然后把自己的遭遇发到网上，强化了大众对该品牌的负面认知。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">2. 用来防尘防水的组件老化或失效</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">iPhone 12 Pro 页面里 IP68 抗水性能的解释是这样的：</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383816" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip13.png" alt="" width="2126" height="582" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip13.png 2126w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip13-360x99.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip13-768x210.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip13-1024x280.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2126px) 100vw, 2126px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">其中有句非常关键的话：防溅、抗水、防尘功能并非永久有效，防护性能可能会因日常磨损而下降。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">硬件的防尘防水功能主要通过硅胶零件、胶水和粘合剂实现，比如不少手机在 SIM 卡槽和音量键等地方用硅胶圈来进行密封，而在空间更小的地方，比如主板和麦克风处，就会首选胶水和粘合剂来做密封。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383818" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip18.jpg" alt="" width="1892" height="1144" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip18.jpg 1892w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip18-360x218.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip18-768x464.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip18-1024x619.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1892px) 100vw, 1892px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ SIM 卡槽内侧有硅胶圈</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383826" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip20.jpg" alt="" width="2180" height="1472" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip20.jpg 2180w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip20-360x243.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip20-768x519.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip20-1024x691.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2180px) 100vw, 2180px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 手机内部的粘合剂</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">这些材料都有两个共同的问题，一是随着自然老化，密封性能会下降，这是无法避免的，二是受到外部环境影响可能失效，比如一次不经意的碰撞或摔打，无数次的热胀冷缩等等。</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">于是我们就看到了有趣的一幕，网上有人觉得某些品牌手机防水性能好，「经常拿着泡澡，觉得脏了就随手洗洗」，「游泳的时候拍水下照片很多次都没事」，「用了一年多了还是经常水洗」，有人却说「太垃圾了不小心沾水就坏了」、「才买不到半年就进水了」等等。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">好事不出门，坏事传千里，正常使用没有翻车的用户是沉默的大多数，但是哪怕只有少量设备进水的情况发生，也会被用户放到网上，造成一种「某品牌手机防水有问题是大规模现象」的假象，这就是幸存者偏差效应。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">3. 商家的释疑不到位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">对于普通用户来说，绝大多数人只会关注商家给出的最显眼的产品表述，很少仔细查看不显眼的小字描述。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">就像牛肉方便面一样，我们看到包装最显眼位置的大块牛肉粒，满怀期待打开包装却发现牛肉碎几乎不可见，会有一种上当受骗的感觉，再仔细看包装，才发现「图片仅供参考」那一行小字。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383827" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip21.png" alt="" width="2384" height="1178" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip21.png 2384w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip21-360x178.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip21-768x379.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip21-1024x506.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2384px) 100vw, 2384px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 没有被方便面骗过的人生是不完美的人生</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">这一点华为和 OPPO 等厂商相较于苹果做得更好一些，在部分手机的产品页面里写明了细节条件：</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383829" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip22.png" alt="" width="2000" height="380" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip22.png 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip22-360x68.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip22-768x146.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip22-1024x195.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 图片来自：华为官网</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">短短三个分句，至少让用户对 IP68 有了更加明晰的认知，实现防水防尘的条件是特定的，IP68 不是「金刚罩铁布衫」，只是一种严谨的标准。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">为何防水手机进水不保修？</span></strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383832" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23.png" alt="" width="2320" height="1298" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23.png 2320w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip23-1024x573.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2320px) 100vw, 2320px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">在讨论这个问题前，我们先用通俗的句子来总结一下 IPXX 是什么。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">它是一种在特定环境和特定条件下测试出来的防尘防水等级标准，可能会随着时间推移和环境条件的改变而失效。</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">这就是「防水手机进水不保修」的第一个难题，防尘防水性能是一种不稳定的状态，手机进水后，无论用户还是商家都很难界定和验证「水是不是在满足 IP68 的条件下进入的」。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">水的纯度和温度是否符合要求，水深多少，浸泡时间多长，手机的防水性能有没有下降等等，商家和用户之间一旦出现了争议基本是无解的。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383851" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip26.png" alt="" width="2318" height="1170" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip26.png 2318w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip26-360x182.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip26-768x388.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip26-1024x517.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2318px) 100vw, 2318px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 日常使用手机的环境很复杂，也和每个人习惯相关</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">其次，灰产和部分用户存在欺骗行为。比如故意让旧的手机进水，再拿去换新或要求无偿维修。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">例如根据硅谷科技媒体 The Information 报道，有两名华裔学生从中国收集损坏甚至是山寨的 iPhone，再到美国苹果官方店「以旧换新」和「以假换新」，涉案金额高达 90 万美元，随后苹果不得不升级售后政策，服务流程变得更加复杂。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">不妨想象一下，如果手机进水就可以免费维修，而一般情况下进水手机基本无法维修，商家只好直接为顾客换新手机，最后的结果是什么？</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"><strong>如果法律规定进水的手机一律保修，本来是出于好意，但在不诚信行为较多的地区，等于变相鼓励不诚信的套利行为，最终的结果就是售后服务越好的商家越容易破产，良币被劣币驱逐</strong>。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383834" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip25.png" alt="" width="2322" height="1296" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip25.png 2322w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip25-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip25-768x429.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ip25-1024x572.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2322px) 100vw, 2322px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">不过，这并不代表厂商可以用「套利行为的存在」这个理由去规避自身的责任，给出更清晰的产品解释和普及 IPXX 标准的满足条件，也是应该履行的义务。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">真正要下功夫的是质检和市场监督环节，保证宣称达到 IP68 防水标准的每一部手机都是合格状态达到消费者手上，才能重建消费者对市场和品牌的信任。</span></p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
